Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A'child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult, no case is left unsolved with Detective Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, Pops and I were helped by Michiyoshi\NMajima, the president of Kiyama Furniture
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when we ran out of gas and got stuck on a mountain pass in Izu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the President, Mr. Majima invited us to stay at his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The house had a Rock Garden.\NIt was so constructed that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,water began to flow and fill the ga den at certain times of the day
